-- Rusal Will Borrow $800 Million to Refinance Debt, Vedomosti Says
-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 2012-08-31T04:06:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-31/rusal-will-borrow-800-million-to-refinance-debt-vedomosti-says.html
United Co. Rusal, a Russian aluminum
producer, plans to borrow $800 million to help refinance debt
due next year,  Vedomosti  reported, citing unidentified people
close to the company and one of the lenders involved in the
talks.  In total, Rusal will have to repay $1.3 billion of debt
next year, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ilya Khrennikov in Moscow at 
 ikhrennikov@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
